title: Batik - Art and Craft (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
pdf / English / 1964 / 76 pages / 9.88 MB

A comprehensive introduction to an age-old technique of fabric decoration. Designed to assist the beginner, the book is inclusive enough to entice the professional as well. Teachers, students, and laymen are clearly shown historical and traditional examples and techniques and are presented with related applications and suggested procedures for exploring the fascinating process of batik
